Welcome to the course repo for Online course starter: dlookr

You can access this course for free online.

This course approaches data diagnosis, EDA, transformation learning using:

  • the dlookr

The interactive course site is built on the amazing framework created by Ines Montani, originally built for her spaCy course. The front-end is powered by Gatsby and the back-end code execution uses Binder.

To learn more about building a course on this framework, see Iness starter repos for making courses in Python and R, and her explanation of how the framework works at the original course repo.
